From MAILER-DAEMON Mon Apr 18 14:25:43 2022
Message-ID: <33354796.1075858674157.JavaMail.evans@thyme>
Date: Mon, 11 Jun 2001 17:56:46 -0700 (PDT)
From: adefelice@ggfcmk.com
To: defelice.anne@enron.com, stremmel.cindy@enron.com, hanken.garrett@enron.com,
	krieger.jeffrey@enron.com, cohen.marc@enron.com
Subject: In re PG&E
Mime-Version: 1.0
