X-From: Hall, Steve C. </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=SHALL4>
X-To: Sanders, Richard B. </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=Rsander>, Belden, Tim </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=Tbelden>, Sager, Elizabeth </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=Esager>, Yoder, Christian </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=Cyoder>, 'gfergus@brobeck.com'
X-cc: 
