Date: Tue, 24 Oct 2000 07:45:00 -0700 (PDT)
From: gfergus@brobeck.com
To: richard.b.sanders@enron.com
Subject: Some thoughts on options
Cc: pmeringolo@brobeck.com
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
Bcc: pmeringolo@brobeck.com
X-From: "Fergus, Gary S." <GFergus@brobeck.com>
X-To: "Richard B. Sanders Esq. (E-mail)" <richard.b.sanders@enron.com>
X-cc: "Meringolo, Peter" <PMeringolo@brobeck.com>
